<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Auroville Community Portal</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            background-color: #f1ece6;
        }

        .sidebar {
            width: 250px;
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: #ecf0f1;
            padding: 20px;
            height: 100vh;
            position: fixed;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }

        .sidebar .logo {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .sidebar-button {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            background-color: #34495e;
            color: #ecf0f1;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: left;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .sidebar-button:hover {
            background-color: #2980b9;
        }

        .sidebar-button i {
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .main-content {
            flex-grow: 1;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-left: 250px;
        }

        .search-bar {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #bdc3c7;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .quick-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .quick-link {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: center;
            flex-basis: 23%;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .quick-link:hover {
            background-color: #2980b9;
        }

        .card {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .card-image {
            width: 100px;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }

        .card-content {
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        .button {
            background-color: #e67e22;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #d35400;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="sidebar">
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="https://aurovillenetwork.org/uploads/default/original/1X/99e32f00cb6f0520758dd2efd953b3628be0efe3.png" alt="Auroville Community Logo" style="max-width: 100%;">
        </div>
        <a href="https://aurovillenetwork.org/u/lucas/activity" class="sidebar-button"><i class="icon-dashboard"></i> Dashboard</a>
        <a href="https://aurovillenetwork.org/c/announcements/5" class="sidebar-button"><i class="icon-announcement"></i> Announcements</a>
        <a href="https://aurovillenetwork.org/c/events/13" class="sidebar-button"><i class="icon-event"></i> Events</a>
        <a href="https://aurovillenetwork.org/categories" class="sidebar-button"><i class="icon-forum"></i> Categories</a>
        <a href="#" class="sidebar-button"><i class="icon-social"></i> Social</a>
        <a href="https://directory.auroville.services/" class="sidebar-button"><i class="icon-directory"></i> Directory</a>
        <a href="#" class="sidebar-button"><i class="icon-references"></i> References</a>
        <a href="#" class="sidebar-button"><i class="icon-help"></i> Help Center</a>
    </div>
    <div class="main-content">
        <input type="text" class="search-bar" placeholder="Search for events, forums, or community resources...">
        <div class="quick-links">
            <a href="#" class="quick-link">Latest News</a>
            <a href="#" class="quick-link">Upcoming Events</a>
            <a href="#" class="quick-link">Community Projects</a>
            <a href="#" class="quick-link">Get Involved</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img src="calendar-icon.png" alt="Calendar" class="card-image">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h2>Events Calendar</h2>
                <p>Stay up-to-date with all the exciting events happening in Auroville. Our easy-to-use calendar helps you find and attend the events that interest you most.</p>
                <button class="button">View all events</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img src="forum-icon.png" alt="Forum" class="card-image">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h2>Community Forums</h2>
                <p>Join the conversation! Our community forums provide a space for respectful discussion on various topics related to Auroville and its development.</p>
                <button class="button">Join the discussion</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img src="directory-icon.png" alt="Directory" class="card-image">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h2>Auroville Directory</h2>
                <p>Find contact information for Auroville's services, businesses, and residents quickly and easily with our comprehensive directory.</p>
                <button class="button">Access Directory</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
